Title: Estorm Technology Pte. Ltd
Template: home
Layout: toppage
Link text: Home

.container-fluid
  .span3
    %a(class="brand" href="/summary")
      %img( src="/attachments/estormcrm.jpg" width=35 height=16 alt='estorm logo')
      = @heading

%section.jumbotron
  %section.hero-unit
    %section.lucky1
      :markdown
        Increase sales and never lose track of customer leads. With EstormTech's process oriented approach to customer management tracking leads and sales activities have never been easier.

        Scratch card data generation and management of scratch cards at the distributor and point of sale level.

        No hidden costs using our affordable monthly subscriptions.  (Our charges are likely less than the cost of your mobile phone bill)

        Distributor and inventory management (managing products at the distributor level)

        Save time and money with a single unified view of customer activities, inventory management including management of time based services.
.container-fluid
  .row-fluid
    .span12
      .carousel(id="myCarousel" class="slide")
        %ol.carousel-indicators
          %li{"data-target"=>"#myCarousel", "data-slide-to"=>"0" ,:class=>"active"}
          - 1.upto(3)  do |k|
            %li{"data-target"=>"#myCarousel", "data-slide-to"=>"#{k}" }
        .carousel-inner
          - [{:link => "/summary",:itemstate=>"active", :caption =>"Estorm Technology Pte. Ltd",:image => "estormmain.jpg", :text =>"Hosted software, technology and other services"},{:link => "/products", :itemstate=>"", :caption =>"Products" ,:image => "products.jpg", :text =>"We deliver software as a service (SAAS) products (CRM/TMS) and other mathematical services like random data for scratch cards"},{:link => "/clients",:itemstate=>"", :caption =>"Clients", :image => "clients.jpg", :text =>"We have a wide range of happy clients that are regionally dispersed (Laos, Philippines, Singapore, Indonesia)"}, {:link => "/contact",:itemstate=>"", :caption =>"Contact Details" , :image => "map2.jpg", :text =>"We are easily contactable and have a conveniently located office in downtown Singapore"}].each do |i|
            .item{:class=> "#{i[:itemstate]}" }
              %img{:src=>"/attachments/#{i[:image]}",  :alt=>"" }
              .container
                .carousel-caption
                  %h2 #{i[:caption]}
                  %p.lead
                    #{i[:text]}
                  %a(href="#{i[:link]}" class="btn btn-large") 
                    Visit #{i[:caption]}
        %a{:class=>"left carousel-control", :href=>"#myCarousel", "data-slide"=>"prev"}
          <
        %a{:class=>"right carousel-control" ,:href=>"#myCarousel", "data-slide"=>"next"}
          >

  .row-fluid
    .span9
      %section.lucky2
        = haml :estorm_users, :layout => false

